# Trivy ignore file — add CVE IDs or misconfiguration IDs to suppress known
# accepted false positives.  Each entry should include a comment explaining
# the reason for suppression and a review date.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # reason — reviewed YYYY-MM-DD
#
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-12345  # only affects feature X which we don't use — reviewed 2026-03-18
